nodes.text: In 188 BBY, the Jedi Padawan Kibh Jeen fell to the dark side of the Force and raised an army of pirates, which he used to wage war against the inhabitants of the Cularin system. The army operated from the Cularin system asteroid belt and under Jeen's direction, they launched a bloody attack on the planet Genarius, which triggered a war that became known as the "Dark Jedi Conflict." The Jedi Order eventually dispatched two Jedi to the Cularin system in 181 BBY, to bring the conflict to a resolution. The Jedi lured Jeen's army into a trap and after a fiercely-fought space battle, the pirates were defeated.
